"27\" height=\"9\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/41px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/54px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></b></li>\n<li><b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://col.org.il/news/135062\">מוסיף והולך: הרב גלויברמן הדליק חנוכייה בערוץ הספורט</a></b> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%95%D7%9F_%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%99%D7%9F\" title=\"חב&quot;ד און ליין\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/15px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/23px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/30px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></li>\n<li><b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://col.org.il/news/129554\">רב חסד</a></b>, כתבה נרחבת ב'ישראל היום' <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%95%D7%9F_%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%99%D7%9F\" title=\"חב&quot;ד און ליין\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/15px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/23px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%